# Code owners for Zoijs.
#
# Every pull request automatically requests a review from the owner(s) below.
# Combined with "Require review from Code Owners" in the `main` branch ruleset,
# this means a maintainer must approve before anything merges.
#
# ⚠️  REPLACE the owner below before this takes effect. Use either:
#   - your GitHub username:                 *  @your-username
#   - an org team you create under Zoijs:   *  @Zoijs/maintainers
# A CODEOWNERS entry pointing at a non-existent user/team is ignored by GitHub.

* @Zoijs/maintainers

# Especially sensitive areas — keep them owned explicitly too:
/.github/          @Zoijs/maintainers
/framework/src/    @Zoijs/maintainers
/router/src/       @Zoijs/maintainers
/resource/src/     @Zoijs/maintainers
/head/src/         @Zoijs/maintainers
/action/src/       @Zoijs/maintainers
